{"tid":165352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邊度有實木買?","createTime":"2017-03-21T09:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T02:49:46.000Z","uid":61699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc11143fa939e078b11ed2402a2bd5e69188fa3","tid":165352,"uid":61699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"想買實木返黎整傢俬，搵左好多間，望落都係得啲夾板，最後都見到有間有現成松木，不過都想睇下有冇其他選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知香港邊度有實木賣? <br />\n松木，柚木，楓木，樺木，胡桃木等等。<br />\n有冇人買過?<br />\n想知現成係咩尺寸，或訂製detail<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b651920a64185ff661ca43084e426e34afba71","tid":165352,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"上山斬咪得囉"},{"pid":"1135cdbbc518b0f2195a0c5cf2592e444d117b86","tid":165352,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"上水有間木廠<br />\n或者木一番"},{"pid":"f3719491b7d7f1f56e69a9107f61b957f3012df5","tid":165352,"uid":61699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T02:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上水有間木廠<br />\n或者木一番</blockquote><br />\n去睇下先"},{"pid":"bd8e7b97a089b3c799dafd0178fdfdb502c23839","tid":165352,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"柳州是最好的"},{"pid":"3c09ddd006c7f7ba1cf6a592100578062204c6fd","tid":165352,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T02:29:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc841ad79f5e354e818ff34f2022a935253be36d","tid":165352,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T02:49:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.jadehome.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jadehome.com.hk&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d8c7f24d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jadehome.com.hk</a>"}]}